&lt;p data-start=&quot;530&quot; data-end=&quot;859&quot;&gt;In this role, the Specialist executes day-to-day digital communications across social media, web, and email platforms. The position focuses on content creation, campaign execution, performance monitoring, and digital engagement, while ensuring consistency with the Agency’s brand, messaging, and public transparency requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
